descriptionHTML:
Always wanted to look into the eye of your smartwatch?! Then this watch face is for you!

Give your smartwatch an eye with this multicolor eye watch face.

With the built-in watch menu and the phone menu in the Android Wear companion app you can easily switch between 12 different eye colors.

The hour and minute hands are inspired by reflections on an eye. The outer reflection circles around the eye, acting as the second hand.

Features:

- Watch face for Android Wear Devices (Moto 360, G Watch R, Gear Live, SmartWatch 3, Huawei Watch, etc.)
- Support for both round and square displays
- 12 different eye colors
- Ambient mode
- Watch menu
- Phone menu

Tip: you can also use this watch face as a Halloween watch face :-)

If you like the app, please leave a good rating!

In case you encounter any issues or have suggestions, email us at support@zappup.nl
